									<p>Then he started the morning discussion with an
										E-Commerce Entrepreneurship topic. Explaining what is
										e-commerce all about. Discussing about the e-commerce laws.
										Talking about e-commerce Company here in the Philippines and
										outside the country. He told the participants what is the
										benefits of entering the e-commerce industry. He also discuss
										about the Pillars of E-Commerce. Explaining what logistics
										means. Talking about marketing and analytics.</p>
									<p>Mr. Nisperos continue the discussion of the Pillars of
